parameters: MTV? What are you doing in LACA?
You fool! You fell for my genius plan!
With all the other obstacles out of the way
Why do you need to control LACA?
Now I can mass produce as many
LACA Bots as I want! And
they can all follow me on Twitter!
So you did this all for more twitter followers?
Because no one would follow you at the school?
You know you can just buy those, right?
needing to take over the whole school
Yes, but now I’m free! Free of the constraints of the school!
Yeah, but now you’re just a robot,
without emotion, so are you really free?
Don’t you want to join me \P[1]?
listen to what you have to say!
You know MTV, before all this,
I didn’t really have anybody to talk to.
But these guys, these are my real followers.
I don’t need some stupid check
I’ve got my friends and that’s all I need!
I’ll just destroy you once I’m verified,
which should be any minute now!
Not if we can help it!
I was mere moments away from perfection.
Thank you guys for helping me.
Maybe you guys aren’t that bad as you seem?
Do you guys know if we have school tomorrow?
